Cash and cash equivalents include €89 million and €164 million as of September 30, 2023 and 2022, respectively, which are not available for use by Siemens mainly due to minimum reserve requirements with banks. As of September 30, 2023, and 2022, the carrying amount of financial assets Siemens pledged as collateral is €164 million and €166 million, respectively.

